# 📝 TODO App

A clean and efficient TODO list web application that helps you organize tasks effortlessly. This project is designed with basic web technologies to provide a smooth and responsive user experience.

🚀 **Live Demo**: [https://todo-app-sigma-azure.vercel.app/]

---

## ✨ Features

- ✅ Add new tasks with ease
- 🗑️ Delete tasks individually
- 📌 Mark tasks as completed or pending
- 🧹 Clear all completed tasks
- 📱 Fully responsive design — works well on mobile and desktop

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- **JavaScript (ES6+)** – Core logic and interactivity
- **HTML5 & CSS3** – Semantic structure and clean styling
- **Vercel** – For seamless deployment and hosting

